+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only
+/*
+ * AMD ACP PCI driver callback routines for ACP6.3, ACP7.0 & ACP7.1
+ * platforms.
+ *
+ * Copyright 2025 Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.
+ * Authors: Vijendar Mukunda <Vijendar.Mukunda@amd.com>
